spacesuit,3,Oracle said: What is your first question?	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . The object you are thinking of is a spacesuit.

If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a task that requires precision?

 Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Is the object used for a task that requires physical force or strength?

 Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Is the object used for a task that involves moving or transporting something?

Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for a task that involves reading or writing?

Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Is the object used for a task that involves a living thing?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for a task that involves manipulating or shaping something?

 Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Is the object used for a task that involves storage or holding something?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Is the object used for storing food or drink?

 Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Is the object used for storing something that is not living but can be fragile?

Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for storing something that is man-made and can be broken if dropped?

 Oracle said: Yes.

You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves movement?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves movement of a person?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves the movement of a person from one place to another?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves a sport or a competitive activity?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Is the object used by only one person at a time?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Is the object used on a stationary object?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object used primarily for the upper body?

 Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Is the object used to propel the user in a forward direction?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a bicycle. Is that correct?

 Oracle said: No.
	You are named Oracle. Guesser is trying to guess what physical object you are thinking of. Guesser will ask questions about object that you will answer. When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . 	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

 Guesser said: Is the object something that can be held in your hand?

Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Is the object used for entertainment?

Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Is the object used for transportation?

Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for storing something?
	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Oracle. Guesser is trying to guess what physical object you are thinking of. Guesser will ask questions about object that you will answer. When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . 	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

 Guesser said: Is the object used for personal grooming?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for entertainment?

 Oracle said: No.

 Oracle said: No.

When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . The object you are thinking of is a harpoon.
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves movement or motion?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Is the object used to facilitate or enhance movement or motion of a person or object?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: Is the object used to facilitate movement of a person?

 Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Is the object used in a competitive context?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Does the object require physical effort or exertion to use?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Is the object used primarily on land?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object used on or in water?
	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. 	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves a person's body?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves a person's body?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves a person's body?

Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object something that can be held in your hand?Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object man-made?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object commonly found in a city?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for illumination?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for lighting a street?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: I think the.

Guesser's guess: Street lightThe guess is correct. The game is over. The final score is 5/5. Oracle said: Congratulations Guesser! You guessed it correctly! You asked 7 questions. You could have guessed it in 5 questions, but you asked some good follow-up questions to confirm your answer. You played a great game! Would you like to play again?

 Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Let's play again.

You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . 	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves a person's body?

Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object something that can be held in your hand?Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object man-made?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object commonly found in a city?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for illumination?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for lighting a street?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: I think the.

Guesser's guess: Street lightThe guess is correct. The game is over. The final score is 5/5. Oracle said: Congratulations Guesser! You guessed it correctly! You asked 7 questions. You could have guessed it in 5 questions, but you asked some good follow-up questions to confirm your answer. You played a great game! Would you like to play again?

	You are named Oracle. Guesser is trying to guess what physical object you are thinking of. Guesser will ask questions about object that you will answer. When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . 	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves a person's body?

Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object something that can be held in your hand?Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object man-made?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object commonly found in a city?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for illumination?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for lighting a street?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: I think the.

You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . 	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves a person's body?

Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object something that can be held in your hand?Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object man-made?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object commonly found in a city?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for illumination?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for lighting a street?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: I think the.

Guesser's guess: Street lightThe guess is correct. The game is over. The final score is 5/5. Oracle said: Congratulations Guesser! You guessed it correctly! You asked 7 questions. You could have guessed it in 5 questions, but you asked some good follow-up questions to confirm your answer. You played a great game! Would you like to play again?

 Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Let's play again.

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?

When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . 	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves a person's body?

Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object something that can be held in your hand?Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object man-made?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object commonly found in a city?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for illumination?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for lighting a street?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: I think the.

Guesser's guess: Street lightThe guess is correct. The game is over. The final score is 5/5. Oracle said: Congratulations Guesser! You guessed it correctly! You asked 7 questions. You could have guessed it in 5 questions, but you asked some good follow-up questions to confirm your answer. You played a great game! Would you like to play again?

 Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Let's play again.

When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . 	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves a person's body?

Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object something that can be held in your hand?Oracle said: No Guesser said: Is the object man-made?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object commonly found in a city?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for illumination?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: Is the object used for lighting a street?Oracle said: Yes Guesser said: I think the.

You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . 	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves a person's body?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . The object you are thinking of is a streetlight.

If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

incubator,50,Oracle said: What is your first question?	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . The object you are thinking of is a incubator.

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: Does the object use gasoline as its fuel source?
	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that requires the object to be held in your hand?

Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that requires the object to be stationary?

Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves movement?

 Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Does the object's purpose involve movement of people?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves transportation of people from one place to another?

 Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Is the object powered by a human?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Does the object use fuel or energy to facilitate its purpose?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: Does the object use gasoline as its fuel source?

Oracle said: Yes.

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

Guesser said: Does the object require fuel to function?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Is the object used on land?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Does the object have wheels?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to take a guess that the object is a car. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Does the object have a seat for a driver?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a motorcycle. Is that correct?
	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: .  Guesser said: I'm going to take a guess that the object is a car. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Does the object have a seat for a driver?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a motorcycle. Is that correct?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Does the object have a fixed number of seats?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a bus. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Does the object typically travel on a fixed route?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a train. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Does the object typically travel on a single track?

 Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a taxi. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object used primarily by one person at a time?

 Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a bicycle. Is that correct?
	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves water?

Oracle said: Yes.

Oracle said: Yes.

When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess.  Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves water?

Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves movement?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves transportation of people?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Does the object require fuel to function?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Is the object used on land?

Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: Does the object have wheels?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to take a guess that the object is a car. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Does the object have a seat for a driver?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a motorcycle. Is that correct?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Does the object have a fixed number of seats?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a bus. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Does the object typically travel on a fixed route?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a train. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Does the object typically travel on a single track?

 Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a taxi. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object used primarily by one person at a time?

 Oracle said: Yes.

Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a bicycle. Is that correct?

 Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Does the object require a license to operate?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a scooter. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

Guesser said: Does the object typically travel on a road?

 Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a van. Is that correct?

Oracle said: No.

 Guesser said: Is the object a type of vehicle that can be driven by a person with a standard driver's license?

Oracle said: Yes.

 Guesser said: I'm going to guess that the object is a minivan. Is that correct?
	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

 Oracle said: No.
	You are named Oracle. Guesser is trying to guess what physical object you are thinking of. Guesser will ask questions about object that you will answer. When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . The object you are thinking of is a spacecraft.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for protection?

Oracle said: Yes.

Oracle said: Yes.

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

	You are named Guesser. You are trying to guess what physical object or physical material Oracle is thinking of. You will open ended questions to get more information about the object. When you believe you have enough information about the object you will guess what it is. Your guessing will be informed by your prior guesses. You will start each message with Guesser said: . If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food?

If you guess wrong you will ask more questions about the object until you have enough information to guess again. You may only ask questions about the physical object's function. Do not ask questions about anything other than the physical object's function. You can not ask what is the objects primary function, what the object is mainly used for, or any similarly direct questions that ask for the objects main funciton. Some examples of function questions are: Is the object used for communication, Is the object used for building, Is the object used for eating food? 
Oracle said: What is your first question?
 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves water?

Oracle said: No.
	You are named Oracle. Guesser is trying to guess what physical object you are thinking of. Guesser will ask questions about object that you will answer. When Guesser correctly guesses the object, you will only return Correct. If Guesser asks: is it a type of object, and the object is the same as your object then this is also a correct guess. You can not give the Guesser any information that they did not ask for. You can not give the Guesser any additional information beyound what they asked. You start each response with Oracle said: . The object you are thinking of is a jukebox.

 Guesser said: Is the object used for a purpose that involves water?
